data.content:
Danh từ
cái khích lệ, điều khich lệ
a morale booster
cái khích lệ tinh thần
máy tăng áp
(cách viết khác booster rocket) tên lửa khởi động
liều thuốc tăng tác dụng; phát tiêm tăng tác dụng

noun
plural -ers
[count] something that boosts someone or something: such as
an action or substance that makes something stronger or more effective
These exercises are real metabolism boosters.
The herb is said to be an immune booster. [=something that strengthens a person's immunity to illness]
something that helps or encourages someone or something
Music is my favorite mood booster.
A sincere compliment can be a true confidence booster.
booster shot
US :someone who supports an idea or organization
The university has a number of wealthy boosters who contribute generously each year.
the football team's boosters
part of a rocket that provides force for the launch and the first part of the flight
a new design for rocket boosters - see also booster seat
